These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
Food: pumpkin, banana, cauliflower, watermelon
1. Food:pumpkin is on the far left##1
2. Food:banana is on the left or right of Food:pumpkin##3
3. Food:banana is on the left or right of Food:cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | pumpkin | banana | cauliflower | watermelon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, sprite, hot-chocolate, lemonade
1. Beverage:mirinda is on the right of Beverage:sprite##1
2. Beverage:lemonade is on the left of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | mirinda | lemonade | hot-chocolate |

 #################################
 
